783
01:19:22,593 --> 01:19:24,072
Cheers.

784
01:19:33,353 --> 01:19:35,628
What were you like as a young man?

785
01:19:36,553 --> 01:19:37,747
Trouble.

786
01:19:40,113 --> 01:19:42,707
-Why?
