Maybe you should.

806
01:22:36,593 --> 01:22:38,424
I found out who Lucy Delaney is.

807
01:22:39,793 --> 01:22:42,432
Remember the Delaneys
from Hillcrest Road?

808
01:22:42,833 --> 01:22:45,506
Yeah, but I thought she died.

809
01:22:46,353 --> 01:22:48,821
