964
01:37:28,473 --> 01:37:32,227
They're practically grown.
You said they hardly talk to you.

965
01:37:32,473 --> 01:37:34,304
Yeah, they don't say much.

966
01:37:35,873 --> 01:37:37,909
But Carolyn is only 16.

967
01:37:40,793 --> 01:37:44,069
She's about to find out
about all of this for herself.

968
01:37:44,313 --> 01:37:46,463
She's going to fall in love...

969
01:37:46,793 --> 01:37:49,910
...and she'll try to
build a life with someone.

970
01:37:53,153 --> 01:37:54,552
