971
01:37:54,793 --> 01:37:56,511
...what does that say to her?

972
01:38:02,953 --> 01:38:04,386
What about us?

973
01:38:05,753 --> 01:38:07,425
You have to know...

974
01:38:08,033 --> 01:38:09,432
...deep down...

975
01:38:09,673 --> 01:38:12,233
...the minute we leave here,
everything will change.

976
01:38:14,393 --> 01:38:16,953
Yeah, it could...
It could get better.

977
01:38:17,193 --> 01:38:21,948
No matter how much distance we put
between ourselves and this house...

978
01:38:23,913 --> 01:38:25,824
...I carry it with me.

979
01:38:27,513 --> 01:38:30,232
I feel it every minute
we're together.

980
01:38:32,873 --> 01:38:36,866
And I will start to blame loving you
for how much it hurts.

981
01:38:37,993 --> 01:38:39,506
And then, even these...

982
01:38:40,393 --> 01:38:41,587
...even these 4...

983
01:38:41,833 --> 01:38:46,065
...beautiful days will seem just like
something sordid and a mistake.

984
01:38:48,153 --> 01:38:52,226
Do you think that what happened with us
just happens to anyone?

985
01:38:53,353 --> 01:38:55,344
What we feel for each other?

986
01:38:56,993 --> 01:38:58,312
We're hardly...

987
01:38:59,273 --> 01:39:01,787
...hardly 2 separate people now.

988
01:39:04,113 --> 01:39:07,662
Some people search all their life
and never find this.

989
01:39:07,913 --> 01:39:09,824
Others don't even think it exists.

990
01:39:10,633 --> 01:39:12,783
You're going to tell me...

991
01:39:13,033 --> 01:39:17,823
You're going to tell me this
is the right thing to do? Giving it up?

992
01:39:20,113 --> 01:39:23,742
We are the choices
that we have made, Robert.

993
01:39:29,753 --> 01:39:31,789
You don't understand.

994
01:39:33,593 --> 01:39:34,867
Don't you see?

995
01:39:35,113 --> 01:39:38,310
Nobody understands when
a woman makes a choice...

996
01:39:38,553 --> 01:39:40,783
...to marry and have children...

997
01:39:41,193 --> 01:39:46,347
...in one way, her life begins,
but in another way, it stops.

998
01:39:47,393 --> 01:39:50,749
You build a life of details...

999
01:39:51,273 --> 01:39:54,743
...and you just stop
and stay steady...

1000
01:39:55,073 --> 01:39:58,270
...so that your children can move.
And when they leave...

1001
01:39:58,513 --> 01:40:01,664
...they take your life of details
with them.

1002
01:40:02,153 --> 01:40:06,465
You're expected to move on,
but you don't remember what moved you...

1003
01:40:06,713 --> 01:40:10,262
...because no one's asked you
in so long, not even yourself.

1004
01:40:14,513 --> 01:40:16,231
But you never think...

1005
01:40:17,033 --> 01:40:20,309
You never think love like this
will happen to you.

1006
01:40:22,393 --> 01:40:24,190
But now that you have it...?

1007
01:40:25,833 --> 01:40:28,825
Now I want to keep it forever.

1008
01:40:29,073 --> 01:40:33,510
I want to love you the way I do now
for the rest of my life...

1009
01:40:35,273 --> 01:40:36,831
...but if we leave...

1010
01:40:37,073 --> 01:40:38,472
...we lose it.

1011
01:40:39,513 --> 01:40:42,550
And I can't make
an entire life disappear...

1012
01:40:42,793 --> 01:40:44,511
...to start a new one.

1013
01:40:44,753 --> 01:40:47,472
All I can do is
try to hold on to us...

1014
01:40:47,713 --> 01:40:49,510
...somewhere inside of me.

1015
01:40:49,753 --> 01:40:51,789
You have to help me.

1016
01:41:04,153 --> 01:41:05,666
Don't lose us.

1017
01:41:06,953 --> 01:41:08,625
Don't throw us away.

1018
01:41:15,233 --> 01:41:17,952
Maybe you feel this way.
Maybe you don't.

1019
01:41:18,793 --> 01:41:21,307
Maybe it's because
you're in this house.

1020
01:41:21,753 --> 01:41:25,666
Maybe tomorrow, when they come back,
you'll feel differently.

1021
01:41:25,913 --> 01:41:28,473
-Don't you think that's possible?
-I don't know.

1022
01:41:31,593 --> 01:41:35,029
Look, I'm going to be here
a few more days.

1023
01:41:35,273 --> 01:41:38,390
We can talk later.
We don't have to decide now.

1024
01:41:40,233 --> 01:41:42,747
Robert, don't!
Don't do this.

1025
01:41:42,993 --> 01:41:45,268
I don't want to say goodbye now.

1026
01:41:45,673 --> 01:41:47,868
We don't have to make that decision.

1027
01:41:48,873 --> 01:41:50,750
